Package: because.phybase
Title: Phylogenetic Structure Module for 'because'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Achaz", "von Hardenberg", , "achaz.hardenberg@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1824-1847"))
Description: Extends the 'because' package with phylogenetic covariance 
    structure support. Implements S3 methods for 'phylo' and 'multiPhylo' 
    objects from the 'ape' package, enabling Bayesian SEM with 
    phylogenetically-structured residuals.
